        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 11 October 2019</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPFORGE-300">HIPFORGE-300</a><br/>
            Upgrade to Bloomreach Experience Manager 13.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="3.1">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 19 June 2019</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPFORGE-286">HIPFORGE-286</a><br/>
            Extend initial login form from LoginForm instead of LoginPanel so the timezone and captcha will show.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="3.0">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 7 February 2019</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Upgrade to BloomReach Experience Manager 12.6</li>
          <li>Rename artifacts to have groupId <code>org.bloomreach.forge.resetpassword</code></li>
          <li>Add Essentials plugin for easy installation</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
