        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 20 October 2016</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Move loginLink to fix visibility of the link.</li>
          <li>Minor upgrade to Hippo 10.2.2</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.1">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 23 September 2016</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Cleaned up error messages when username unknown.</li>
          <li>Dependency optimizations.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.0">
